Yocto in Python 2
Yocto is developed by the Linux foudnation which is the main organization for Linux development

a central Yocto project defines the baseline with the HASH used an each repository
It relieves continuous integration.
you only need to build jenkins for the baseline change not all the small repos. This allows many intermediate commits.

